Timelapse Controller
Control the timelaspe settings for the Raspberry Pi.

1. git clone ...
2. sudo ln -s ... /home/timelapsecontroller
3. # check perms
4. cd /home/timelapsecontroller/bin/ ; python setup.py # do setup

5. Run the standalone flask startup file
pi@raspberrypi /home/timelapsecontroller $ python index.py 
 * Running on http://0.0.0.0:5000/ (Press CTRL+C to quit)
 * Restarting with stat

6. Browse to http://10.0.0.8:5000/
7. Kickup the backend job (needs root for access to /dev/mem)

pi@raspberrypi sudo /home/timelapsecontroller/bin $ python focusandshoot.py 
Sleeping for 2 seconds..
Sleeping for 2 seconds..

